      <p>
       Consider Moodle your “base camp” for this course.  All information, assignments, updates, Zoom links, etc. will be posted there.  If you have a question, it's probably answered on Moodle (perhaps in this very syllabus...).  I expect you to check the site frequently to stay on top of deadlines and course communications.
